'''Radical Entertainment'''，是总部设在加拿大不列颠哥伦比亚省温哥华的游戏开发商。它成立于1991年，先前的游戏由其他游戏发行商发行。2005年，该工作室被维旺迪游戏收购，现在为动视暴雪的子公司。<ref>2005-03-23. Gamers Hell: http://www.gamershell.com/companies/v_u_g_/220157.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamershell.com/companies/v_u_g_/220157.html |date=20120403011109 }}</ref>该工作室是不列颠哥伦比亚省最古老的游戏工作室，一个完全拥有的子公司，常常被称为温哥华游戏业中的骨干力量。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theprovince.com/life/laid+Vancouver+video+game+company+Radical+Entertainment/6858008/story.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103153302/http://www.theprovince.com/life/laid+Vancouver+video+game+company+Radical+Entertainment/6858008/story.html |archivedate=2012-11-03 }}</ref>

该工作室在2012年6月28日进行大幅裁员导致不能制作原创游戏，并用来支持动视的游戏作品，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/prototype_2/news/radical_entertainment_has_closed.html|title=Radical Entertainment has closed|accessdate=28 June 2012|archive-date=2015-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921141154/http://www.videogamer.com/xbox360/prototype_2/news/radical_entertainment_has_closed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>裁员的原因是因为温哥华的游戏设计市场陨落<ref>{{cite news|last=Siemiatycki|first=Elliot|title=Tactical change necessary to retain video game industry|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/technology/gaming/Tactical+change+necessary+retain+video+game+industry/6955632/story.html|newspaper=Vancouver Sun|date=July 20, 2012|accessdate=2015-11-04|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805125819/http://www.vancouversun.com/technology/gaming/Tactical+change+necessary+retain+video+game+industry/6955632/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不过，后来证实裁员并不是那么严重。<ref name="twitter.com">{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/Radical_Ent/status/248450258655379456 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211417/https://twitter.com/Radical_Ent/status/248450258655379456 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

